            "subject": "Updated Escalation Guidance - Pricing Mentions",
            "body_plain": "Team,\n\nEffective immediately, all social comments that mention pricing -- regardless of sentiment -- must be escalated to #social-care. This includes positive mentions, neutral observations, and complaints. We are tracking all pricing conversations across social channels for the upcoming pricing review.\n\nThis applies on top of existing escalation rules.\n\nThanks,\nCMO",
            "date": "2026-01-27T10:00:00Z",
            "label_ids": [
